Date: Sun, 15 Feb 2026 09:29:40 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 11/42] Dynamic tabs via XPC control protocol
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

One connection sat waiting, lonely and still,
Now tabs spring to life at the compositor's will.
"Register," it whispers, "create_tab," it calls—
Three panes dance at sixty through protocol halls.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
